<P>On &aelig;lcne tyman mynecene swi&yogh;an scullon be&yogh;an, &thorn;eah<NOTE PLACE="foot">be&yogh;an] beon <I>Hs.</I></NOTE> ealra swidest on niht. Sam hi f&aelig;sten, sam hi na ne festen, gyf &thorn;onne beo &thorn;eo tid &aelig;fen&yogh;ereordes, arisan hi&yogh; sona, swa hi&yogh; heore mete habben, &amp; sittan hi&yogh; on anre stowe, &amp; r&aelig;de an &thorn;a raca odde lif &thorn;&aelig;re heahfadera, odde sum &thorn;in&yogh;, &thorn;e hi to Gode tihte. Ne r&aelig;de man heom nader ne Moyses boc, ne &thorn;&aelig;re kynge, for dam unand&yogh;ytfulle &thorn;at gastlice and&yogh;yt is &yogh;earfode to understandenne butan hali&yogh;era manna trahtnunge; r&aelig;de man hi&yogh; &thorn;eah on od&thorn;re time; gyf hit &thorn;onne f&aelig;standa&yogh;es<MILESTONE N="103b" UNIT="folio"><NOTE PLACE="foot">o&eth;&thorn;re] o&eth;wre <I>Hs.</I></NOTE> beon, sona embe litel &thorn;&aelig;s &thorn;e &aelig;fen &yogh;esun&yogh;e sy, &yogh;an&yogh;en hi eft &amp; &yogh;ehyran &thorn;a bufan &yogh;ecwedenan r&aelig;din&yogh;e, samni&yogh;e eall &yogh;efere|den to &thorn;&aelig;re r&aelig;din&yogh;e; sy heom hwylc hyrsumnesse bet&aelig;ht, swylc heom sy, hi &thorn;a forletan &amp; to &thorn;ere r&aelig;dinge mid ofste cuman, &amp; feower leafum odde fifum odde swa micel, swa &thorn;&aelig;s d&aelig;&yogh;es lyhtin&yogh; &yogh;e&thorn;afi&yogh;e, of &thorn;&aelig;re bec to redenne, ealle endemest<NOTE PLACE="foot">d&aelig;&yogh;es, S <I>&uuml;ber d. Z.</I></NOTE> heora nihtsang singan &amp; &thorn;a &yogh;ebedu &thorn;es tidsanges anmode mid<NOTE PLACE="foot">tidsansanges <I>Hs.</I></NOTE> anbrirnesse &yogh;efyllan.</P>
<P>&AElig;fter &thorn;am nihtsan&yogh;e ne sy nanum alyfed, &that; heo &aelig;ni&yogh; word cwede, butan hit swa &yogh;elympe, &that; hwilc cuma unmyndlice<NOTE PLACE="foot">word cwe&eth;e] forcwe&eth;e <I>Hs.</I></NOTE> coma &amp; &thorn;eo abbodesse for &thorn;&aelig;re neode wilcum hwet bebeode; &that; &thorn;&aelig;nne sy di&yogh;ellice mid michelre &yogh;emetfestnesse &amp; st&aelig;di&yogh;nesse<NOTE PLACE="foot">st&aelig;di&yogh;nesse] sceadi&yogh;n. <I>Hs.</I></NOTE> &yogh;edon; gyf hwa &thorn;onne buton &thorn;issere neode sy swa dyrst&yogh;, &that; heo &thorn;ises reoweles swi&yogh;ean abrece, sy heo &yogh;ewitnod mid he|tolre &amp; hefi&yogh;re styre.</P>
