<DIV2 N="45" TYPE="chapter">
<HEAD>XLV. BE &THORN;AN &THORN;E ON MUNSTRE MYSSE&ETH; OD&ETH; MISFO&ETH;.<MILESTONE N="107a" UNIT="folio"><NOTE PLACE="foot">MYSSE&ETH;] mysted <I>Hs.</I> &Verbar; MISFO&ETH;] miswod <I>Hs.</I></NOTE></HEAD>
