<PB REF="00000125.tif" N="97"><MILESTONE UNIT="A" N="72,4-73,10"></P>
<P>Gyf hit &thorn;onne hyra sawla &yogh;yltes beod, &thorn;e odre mann&aelig; di&yogh;ele beod &amp; hyre sylfre cud, mid hyre andeatnysse unwreo hi&yogh; hyre abbodesse odde sumre gastlicre swuster, &thorn;e holuast<NOTE PLACE="foot">holuast] <I>zwischen</I> hol- <I>und</I> uast <I>Rasur eines Buchst., wie es scheint</I> &yogh;.</NOTE> sy &amp; hyra sawla wunde h&aelig;lean cunne &amp; odre manna, &amp; na un|wreo<NOTE PLACE="foot">h&aelig;lean] h&aelig;lcan <I>Hs.</I></NOTE> odde widmersian.<NOTE PLACE="foot">widnersian <I>Hs.</I></NOTE></P>
