<P>Sy &thorn;&aelig;re abbodesse &yogh;yemen d&aelig;&yogh;es &amp; nihtes, &that; man ealle &yogh;etida &thorn;es godcundan &thorn;eoudomes on rihtne timan &amp; &yogh;edafen|lice<MILESTONE N="108a" UNIT="folio"> hrin&yogh;e, odde heo sylf &aelig;lce tide hringe, odde swylcere carefullan swuster &thorn;a &yogh;emene bet&aelig;ce, &thorn;e &aelig;lce tide on rihtne<NOTE PLACE="foot">rihne <I>Hs.</I></NOTE> time mid beacne &yogh;eswuteli&yogh;e &amp; nane tid &thorn;&aelig;s godcundan weorces<NOTE PLACE="foot">beacne, c <I>&uuml;ber der Z.</I> &Verbar; &yogh;eswuteli&yogh;e] &yogh;eswu- <I>Zeilenschluss</I> -swuteli&yogh;e <I>Hs.</I></NOTE> ne for&yogh;ymelesie.</P>
<P>Sealmes &amp; antifenes be endebirdnesse &aelig;fter &thorn;&aelig;re abbodesse be&yogh;ynne, &thorn;a &thorn;e hit &yogh;eboden byd. Ne &yogh;edyrstl&aelig;ce hyre &aelig;ni&yogh; &that; heo ador do, odde singe, odde rede, buton heo &thorn;a &thorn;enunge for&thorn;bringe m&aelig;&yogh;e, swa &thorn;&aelig;t heo &thorn;a &yogh;etimbri&yogh;e &amp; naht ne &yogh;edrefe<NOTE PLACE="foot">for&thorn;bringe] forhbr. <I>Hs.</I></NOTE> &thorn;a &thorn;e hi &yogh;ehired; &amp; &thorn;&aelig;t beo &yogh;edon mid eadmodnesse &amp; ho&yogh;en &amp; ei&yogh;e, &amp; &thorn;a hit don, &thorn;e &thorn;eo abbodesse hate.</P>
